desc_short	-----								Awaken on an asteroid in deep space, underneath comets and giant stars. Designed exclusively for room-scale VR, Prologue introduces the critically-acclaimed world of Irrational Exuberance—a fever dream of interstellar interactions. Take the first step on a journey of risk, wonder and discovery.							
developer									Buffalo Vision								
